14 ········This·repository·provides·code·that·enables·access·to·different·forms·of·life·cycle·

18 ········

20 ········LCA·software.··However,·the·plan·is·to·remove·this·requirement·by·off-loading· 
21 ········computing·requirements·to·the·cloud.··· 
22 ········ 
23 ········##·Additional·Packages 
24 ········

27 ········[antelope_background](https://github.com/AntelopeLCA/background).··The·idea·is·that· 
28 ········these·computations·can·be·performed·remotely,·allowing·lightweight·clients·to·run
